  "time_ut": 1662019178,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The prices of tobacco have skyrocketed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been increased by Rs.3, Rs.5, Rs.10 and Rs.15 from today. As excise duty has been increased from today (01), the prices of tobacco products have also been increased.",
        "It is noteworthy that the income tax has been increased from 12 percent to 15 percent through the interim budget."
      ],
